nodes.text: A gene farm was a location that the Ugnaught moisture farmer Kuiil worked in at some point in his life. In 9 ABY,[source?] Mandalorian bounty hunter Din Djarin, Carasynthia Dune, and Kuill discussed the origins of the sentient being known as The Child, when Djarin brought up that The Child could be a Strand-Cast, Kuiil dismissed it mentioning that he had worked in gene farms previously.
